title: Sven Fischer (footballer)
text:
Sven Fischer (born 7 January 1977 in <a href="Weiterstadt">Weiterstadt</a>) is a retired German <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="Defender%20%28association%20football%29">defender</a>.
Fischer made two appearances in the <a href="2.%20Bundesliga">2. Bundesliga</a> for <a href="Hannover%2096">Hannover 96</a>.
He represented Germany at the <a href="1995%20FIFA%20World%20Youth%20Championship">1995 FIFA World Youth Championship</a>.
